**Download latest tomcat

**Unzip in tmp
tar xvzf apache-tomcat*.tar.gz -C /tmp/

**Change Ownership and Move to opt
sudo su -c "chown -R root:root /tmp/apache-tomcat-7.0.63 && mv /tmp/apache-tomcat-7.0.63 /opt/apache-tomcat-7.0.63"


**Staring Server
/opt/apache-tomcat-7*/bin/startup.sh

**Stopping Server
/opt/apache-tomcat-7*/bin/shutdown.sh

**Localhost Port
localhost:8080